  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Keystore folder has moved from Appdata\\Roaming\\Ethereum to Appdata\\Roaming\\Mist\\\n\nIs this a permanent move? if so, the Ethereum wallet accounts>Backup>Accounts .... points to the wrong location (it still points to AppData\\Roaming\\Ethereum) \n\nAlso unless the keystore folder iscopied from AppData\\Roaming\\Ethereum  to AppData\\Roaming\\Mist\\\n,  Ethereum wallet version 0.8.4 tells you that no account has been made.  Once keystore folder has been copied over from old location to new location Ethereum wallet recognises it.\n",
